   IGNET

                                 OIG Hotmail

   Employees are in the best position to detect problems in their
   workplace and they can help the Office of Inspector General improve
   management and eliminate fraud. The NSF OIG encourages all employees to
   help improve government by providing information to OIG about fraud,
   waste, misconduct, abuse, and unnecessary government expenditures.

   For more information write:

     National Science Foundation
     Office of Inspector General
     4201 Wilson Boulevard, Suite 1135
     Arlington, VA 22230

   or call 800-428-2189

   or visit our electronic mail hotline at oig@nsf.gov

